quran[8{c,v,t}:
10,7,jin logon ko hum se milnay ki tawaqqa nahi aur duniya ki zindagi se khush aur isi par mtymn ho baithy aur hamari nishanion se ghaafil ho rahay hain
10,8,un ka thikana un ( aamaal ) ke sabab jo woh karte hain dozakh hai
10,9,aur jo log imaan laaye aur naik kaam karte rahay un ko perwar-digaar un ke imaan ki wajah se ( aisay mehloon ki ) raah dukhaay ga ( ke ) un ke neechay Nemat ke baghoon mein nehrein beh rahi hon gi
10,10,( jab woh ) un mein ( un nematon ko daikhon ge to be sakhta ) kahin ge subhan allah. aur aapas mein un ki dua salam alaikum hogi aur un ka aakhri qoul yeh ( hoga ) ke khuday-e rab alameen ki hamd ( aur is ka shukar ) hai
10,11,aur agar khuda logon ki buraiee mein jaldi karta jis terhan woh talab kher mein jaldi karte hain. to un ki ( Umar ki ) meyaad poori hochuki hoti so jin logon ko hum se milnay ki tawaqqa nahi inhen hum chhorey rakhtay hain ke apni sar kashi mein behektey rahen
10,12,aur jab ensaan ko takleef pahunchti hai to leyta aur betha aur khara ( har haal mein ) hamein pukaarta hai. phir jab hum is takleef ko is se daur kar dete hain to ( be lehaaz ho jata hai aur ) is terhan guzar jata hai goya kisi takleef pounchanay par hamein kabhi puraka hi nah tha. isi terhan hadd se nikal jaane walon ko un ke aamaal aaraasta karkay dukhaay gay hain
10,13,aur tum se pehlay hum kayi amton ko jab unhon ne zulm ka rasta ikhtiyarkiya halaak kar chukay hain. aur un ke paas paighambar khuli nishanain le kar aeye magar woh aisay nah they ke imaan laatay. hum gunehgaar logon ko isi terhan badla diya karte hain
10,14,phir hum ne un ke baad tum logon ko malik mein khalifa banaya taakay dekhen tum kaisay kaam karte ho
